<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>七律 on Script Adults</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/tags/%E4%B8%83%E5%BE%8B/</link><description>Recent content in 七律 on Script Adults</description><image><title>Script Adults</title><url>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/images/papermod-cover.png</url><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/images/papermod-cover.png</link></image><generator>Hugo -- 0.128.2</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 01:35:25 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://katsuragicsl.github.io/tags/%E4%B8%83%E5%BE%8B/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>見族人炫祖上之富</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%A6%8B%E6%97%8F%E4%BA%BA%E7%82%AB%E7%A5%96%E4%B8%8A%E4%B9%8B%E5%AF%8C/</link><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 01:35:25 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%A6%8B%E6%97%8F%E4%BA%BA%E7%82%AB%E7%A5%96%E4%B8%8A%E4%B9%8B%E5%AF%8C/</guid><description>誰家三水田千里，舊榭新軒盡姓陳。
輒耀膏粱矜祖富，詩書少讀曝詞貧。
詢其祖業餘多少，賞彼紅腮半怯嗔。
渴鬼愁看舊時屋，年年祭饗供他人。</description></item><item><title>無題</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%84%A1%E9%A1%8C/</link><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 22:33:12 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%84%A1%E9%A1%8C/</guid><description>陳衣欲搗子規啼，嗽穿重簾夜更淒。
十載茅齋茂陵臥，雙行枯淚太常妻。
清心昔捨青雲路，俗務今催洗耳溪。
半世徒勞芳自賞，來生捨筆執鋤犁。</description></item><item><title>李恥杜愁</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%9D%8E%E6%81%A5%E6%9D%9C%E6%84%81/</link><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 22:01:14 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%9D%8E%E6%81%A5%E6%9D%9C%E6%84%81/</guid><description>性俗全無墨在胸，冥搜拙句砌機峰。
詩成引得謫仙恥，筆落愁催工部容。
既與深情詩韻繫，何教秉賦櫟樗庸。
如吾堪作違心事，簡朽帛殘枯筆封。</description></item><item><title>古不賤今</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%8F%A4%E4%B8%8D%E8%B3%A4%E4%BB%8A/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%8F%A4%E4%B8%8D%E8%B3%A4%E4%BB%8A/</guid><description>人常詠古歌仁聖，似是今人鄙不勝。
叔夜孤高難仿效，夷齊朽滯若瘕癥。
西山槁槁饑薇蕨，一曲淒淒絕廣陵。
史內千秋寸心辨，賢愚莫有固規繩。</description></item></channel></rss>